txt.en: You have defeated many goblins at Bâr Faroth.
Goblins can be found at Bâr Faroth in Yondershire.\n\nWhile exploring the Yondershire, you have encountered goblins at Bâr Faroth. You should defeat goblins at Bâr Faroth.

You have done much to hinder the goblins in their efforts to capture Bâr Faroth. Although many of their number remain encamped in its eastern reaches, few still dare to brave the span into the western ruins of Bâr Faroth.

While exploring the Yondershire, you have encountered a number of goblins exploring the ruins of Bâr Faroth. Although they have seemingly captured the eastern ruins of Bâr Faroth, only a few have ventured into the western ruins. However, if these goblins are not defeated, it is likely they will soon lay claim to all of Bâr Faroth.\n\nYou should defeat goblins at the ruins of Bâr Faroth.
Goblins have begun to settle in the ruins of Bâr Faroth, much to the dismay of the inhabitants of the Yondershire.
